input: Subject: A sleek modern kitchen; Characteristics: stainless steel appliances and minimalist design; Timing and lighting: daytime with bright lighting; Background: open-plan space with marble countertops; Feeling: clean and efficient.
output: A sleek modern kitchen features starkly contrasting pristine stainless steel appliances against a backdrop of subtle, high-gloss white cabinetry in a minimalist design. Daylight floods through large windows, casting a vibrant, bright light across the open-plan space adorned with polished marble countertops. The scene pulses with clean lines and efficient functionality, exuding a tranquil sense of efficiency and modern elegance.
